snippet.title: Wyld Land - Demo Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3387720/Wyld_Land/
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/7yPh4FYXyu

Wyld Land is a bullet hell MMO inspired by games like Enter the Gungeon, Archvale, Nuclear Throne, and Realm of the Mad God. Play the demo and Wishlist on Steam now!

#WyldLand #bullethell #indiegame #mmo #roguelike
